        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n          \n        \n      \n    \n\n    Mon Jul 6, 2026 • 7:00pm\n\n  \n          Film\n    \n          Anime\n      \n\n  Event length: 94 minutes\n\n      Admission $12.50\n    \n      Ticket prices include all taxes and fees.\n    \n  \n\n\n      \n  \n    Buy tickets\n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n  \n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n    \n      \n                  Studio Ghibli: Porco Rosso\n        \n                  \n            Rating: PG | Country: Japan | Languages: English | Year: 1992 // In Italy in the 1930s, sky pirates in biplanes terrorize wealthy cruise ships as they sail the Adriatic Sea. The only pilot brave enough to stop the scourge is the mysterious Porco Rosso (Shuichiro Moriyama), a former World War I flying ace who was somehow turned into a pig during the war. As he prepares to battle the pirate crew's American ace, Porco Rosso enlists the help of spunky girl mechanic Fio Piccolo (Akemi Okamura) and his longtime friend Madame Gina (Tokiko Kato).\n          \n        \n              \n\n      \n  \n    Event Info\n\n          \n        Category: Film      \n    \n          \n        Genre: Anime      \n    \n          \n        Event Length: 94 minutes\n      \n    \n      \n  \n  \t\t\n\n\n      \n      Venue\n\n              Imperial Theatre\n      \n              12 King Square South, Saint John NB, E2L 5B8\n      \n              \n          \n            View on Google Maps\n          \n        \n          \n  \n  \n\n\n\n{\n    \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n    \"@type\": \"Event\",\n    \"@id\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/studio-ghibli-porco-rosso/33801ASNTMSCGCRRHSPSCJNKGBMBPNMSP/#event-33801asntmscgcrrhspscjnkgbmbpnmsp\",\n    \"name\": \"Studio Ghibli: Porco Rosso\",\n    \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/studio-ghibli-porco-rosso/33801ASNTMSCGCRRHSPSCJNKGBMBPNMSP/\",\n    \"eventAttendanceMode\": \"https://schem