    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "$12.50 // Rating: PG | Country: Japan | Languages: English | Year: 2004 // Sophie (Emily Mortimer) has an uneventful life at her late father's hat shop, but all that changes when she befriends wizard Howl (Christian Bale), who lives in a magical flying castle. However, the evil Witch of Waste (Lauren Bacall) takes issue with their budding relationship and casts a spell on young Sophie, which ages her prematurely. Now Howl must use all his magical talents to battle the jealous hag and return Sophie to her former youth and beauty."
      }
