        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n          \n        \n      \n    \n\n    Mon Jul 27, 2026 • 7:00pm\n\n  \n          Film\n    \n          Anime\n      \n\n  Event length: 170 minutes\n\n      Admission $12.50\n    \n      Ticket prices include all taxes and fees.\n    \n  \n\n\n      \n  \n    Buy tickets\n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n  \n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n    \n      \n                  Studio Ghibli: Spirited Away: Live On Stage\n        \n                  \n            Rating: PG | Country: Japan | Languages: English | Year: 2002 // Hayao Miyazaki’s Academy Award®-winning animated feature film comes to life in this first-ever stage adaptation, full of dazzling sets, captivating musical numbers, and wondrous puppets of beloved characters. Adapted and directed by Tony Award®-winner John Caird (Les Misérables), two unique casts and performances were filmed during the show’s acclaimed 2022 run at Tokyo’s historic Imperial Theatre, featuring Kanna Hashimoto and Mone Kamishiraishi as Chihiro.\n          \n        \n              \n\n      \n  \n    Event Info\n\n          \n        Category: Film      \n    \n          \n        Genre: Anime      \n    \n          \n        Event Length: 170 minutes\n      \n    \n      \n  \n  \t\t\n\n\n      \n      Venue\n\n              Imperial Theatre\n      \n              12 King Square South, Saint John NB, E2L 5B8\n      \n              \n          \n            View on Google Maps\n          \n        \n          \n  \n  \n\n\n\n{\n    \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n    \"@type\": \"Event\",\n    \"@id\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/studio-ghibli-spirited-away-live-on-stage/34401AVSCHHTDLGCSLVJRSQLBPTLHDKLB/#event-34401avschhtdlgcslvjrsqlbptlhdklb\",\n    \"name\": \"Studio Ghibli: Spirited Away: Live On Stage\",\n    \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/studio-ghibli-spirited-away-live-on