    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Thane Dunn's New ELVIS in Concert"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Admission $54.75 // Canada's Water Jano Water proudly presents The Ultimate Elvis in Concert Experience! Get ready for an electrifying, high-energy journey through the musical legacy of Elvis Presley. Thane Dunn's brand-new \"Elvis in Concert\" production marks his triumphant return to the Imperial Theatre stage. Bringing the passion, the power, and the unmistakable charisma of the King to life in a way that will leave you breathless. This new show is a masterclass in Rock & Roll history. The Two-time World Champion Elvis tribute artist delivers unmatched vocal accuracy, stage presence, and authentic style. Every detail has been meticulously crafted—featuring stunning, screen-accurate replica jumpsuits and a production value that matches the scale of Vegas. His audience interaction and stage presence are unmistakably Elvis-like. Its like watching the real thing live before your eyes. The Magic Behind the Music Besides Dunn's stunning Elvis look, sound, moves, and charisma what also sets this show apart is the music. Backing the performance is a brand-new, hand-picked powerhouse band that has already earned rave reviews. Replicating the driving rhythm and wall-of-sound energy of Elvis’s legendary TCB Band, these world-class musicians deliver the groove and the rock-solid foundation that made Presley’s live shows legendary. This isn't just a tribute; it’s a living, breathing concert experience officially recognized for its authenticity and dedication to keeping the spark of the King alive. Whether you're a lifelong fan who remembers the magic the first time around, or a new generation experiencing the power of his music for the first time, this is the show you cannot afford to miss. Fun for Elvis fans of all ages."
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/eventAttendanceMode": [
      {
        "@id": "http://schema.org/OfflineEventAttendanceMode"
      }
    ],
