        "@value": "A Seating $85.00 | B Seating $80.00 | C Seating $75.00 // Back by popular demand, Come From Away soars across New Brunswick! Performed by an all New Brunswick cast, including Broadway’s Tony LePage, this heartwarming, funny, and foot-stomping musical tells the true story of kindness in Gander, Newfoundland after 9/11. Don’t miss this joyful, unforgettable celebration of community! Presented by Saint John Theatre Company & Rogue Productions, Come From Away celebrates the power of community onstage, offstage, and at home."
      }
