    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Advance P1 $56.25 | P2 $51.25 | P3 $46.25 ~ Day of P1 $61.25 | P2 $56.25| P3 $51.25 // All the way from Cape Breton Island, the girls head out on their first cross-Canada tour. Come see the viral East Coast duo as they bring their signature storytelling and off the cuff humour to the stage. If you’re missing home or just want a good laugh, Tracy and Martina deliver every time. With stories, crowd interaction, and plenty of surprise moments, it’s a night you won’t forget! https://www.tracyandmartina.com/"
      }
    ],
