        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n          \n        \n      \n    \n\n    Fri Sep 25, 2026 • 8:00pm\n\n  \n          Comedy\n    \n          Stand Up\n      \n\n  Event length: 120 minutes\n\n      Admission $56.25 | Admission $51.25 | Admission $46.25\n    \n      Ticket prices include all taxes and fees.\n    \n  \n\n\n      \n  \n    Buy tickets\n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n  \n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n    \n      \n                  Tracy & Martina: Live\n        \n                  \n            Advance P1 $56.25 | P2 $51.25 | P3 $46.25 ~ Day of P1 $61.25 | P2 $56.25| P3 $51.25 // All the way from Cape Breton Island, the girls head out on their first cross-Canada tour. Come see the viral East Coast duo as they bring their signature storytelling and off the cuff humour to the stage. If you’re missing home or just want a good laugh, Tracy and Martina deliver every time. With stories, crowd interaction, and plenty of surprise moments, it’s a night you won’t forget! https://www.tracyandmartina.com/\n          \n        \n              \n\n      \n  \n    Event Info\n\n          \n        Category: Comedy      \n    \n          \n        Genre: Stand Up      \n    \n          \n        Event Length: 120 minutes\n      \n    \n      \n  \n  \t\t\n\n\n      \n      Venue\n\n              Imperial Theatre\n      \n              12 King Square South, Saint John NB, E2L 5B8\n      \n              \n          \n            View on Google Maps\n          \n        \n          \n  \n  \n\n\n\n{\n    \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n    \"@type\": \"Event\",\n    \"@id\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/tracy-martina-live/31001ANSGMCKVDLMTPSRQHVNSMPTMDPCG/#event-31001ansgmckvdlmtpsrqhvnsmptmdpcg\",\n    \"name\": \"Tracy & Martina: Live\",\n    \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/tracy-martina-live/31001ANSGMCKVDLMTPSRQHVNSMPTMDPCG/\",\n    \"eventAttendanceMode\": \"https://schema.org/OfflineEventAttendanceMode\",\n    \"eventStatus\": \"https://schema.org/EventScheduled\",\n    \"location\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Place\",\n        \"name\": \"Imperial Theatre\",\n        \"sameAs\": [\n            \"http://kg.artsdata.ca/resource/K11-193\",\n            \"http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q3527482\"\n        ],\n        \"address\": {\n            \"@type\": \"PostalAddress\",\n            \"streetAddress\": \"12 King Square South\",\n            \"addressLocality\": \"Saint John\",\n            \"postalCode\": \"E2L 5B8\",\n            \"addressRegion\": \"New Brunswick\",\n            \"addressCountry\": {\n                \"@type\": \"Country\",\n                \"name\": \"CA\"\n            }\n        }\n    },\n    \"organizer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Imperial Theatre\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/\"\n    },\n    \"description\": \"Advance P1 $56.25 | P2 $51.25 | P3 $46.25 ~ Day of P1 $61.25 | P2 $56.25| P3 $51.25 // All the way from Cape Breton Island, the girls head out on their first cross-Canada tour. Come see the viral East Coast duo as they bring their signature storytelling and off the cuff humour to the stage. If you’re missing home or just want a good laugh, Tracy and Martina deliver every time. With stories, crowd interaction, and plenty of surprise moments, it’s a night you won’t forget! https://www.tracyandmartina.com/\",\n    \"image\": [\n        \"https://system.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/files/2c5f6c42-be0d-430a-8a8f-44ada7827a42.jpeg\"\n    ],\n    \"startDate\": \"2026-09-25T17:00:00-03:00\",\n    \"offers\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Offer\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatrenewbrunswick.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/website/EventDetails.aspx?EventId=31001ANSGMCKVDLMTPSRQHVNSMPTMDPCG\",\n        \"availability\": \"https://schema.org/InStock\",\n        \"validFrom\": \"2026-09-25T17:00:00-03:00\"\n    },\n    \"performer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Thing\",\n        \"additionalType\": [\n            \"http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Agent\",\n            \"http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Agent\"\n        ],\n        \"name\": \"Tracy & Martina: Live\"\n    }\n}\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t"
