        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n          \n        \n      \n    \n\n    Sat Oct 10, 2026 • 7:30pm\n\n  \n          Music\n    \n          Tribute\n      \n\n  Event length: 120 minutes\n\n      Admission $56.25\n    \n      Ticket prices include all taxes and fees.\n    \n  \n\n\n      \n  \n    Buy tickets\n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n  \n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n    \n      \n                  Solitary Man: Celebrating the Music of Neil Diamond\n        \n                  \n            \n\t$56.25 // TIME WARP PROMOTIONS PRESENTS SOLITARY MAN - CELEBRATING THE MUSIC OF NEIL DIAMOND. Will Chalmers is a multi award winning tribute artist and has been in the music industry for over 30 years. He has been performing his Neil Diamond tribute since 2002 and has also performed tributes to Garth Brooks, Conway Twitty, John Lennon and Elvis. He is also part of the Highwaymen Tribute Forever Highwaymen portraying the role of Waylon Jennings. ◦ Will has traveled with his band all over the USA. Canada and also performed in Mexico, Cayman Islands and Europe. Willʼs natural resemblance to Neil Diamond, his flawless replication of Neilʼs singing voice, combined with his outstanding stage presence has been captivating audiences wherever he goes. The response from Neil fans has been an unbelievable experience. Will is both friendly and personable and people approach him with ease, he is always available to speak to people after the performance and welcomes their comments. ◦ Neil Diamond is a Living Legend and it is with much respect and admiration for the singer songwriter that Will Chalmers tribute is performed. People leave the show with a smile on their face and a song in their hearts. https://www.theneildiamondtributeshow.com/WATCH HERE:  Solitary Man\n\n          \n        \n              \n\n      \n  \n    Event Info\n\n          \n        Category: Music      \n    \n          \n        Genre: Tribute      \n    \n          \n        Event Length: 120 minutes\n      \n    \n      \n  \n  \t  \t  \n    \tPerformer Website:\n    \t\n      Visit Website\n    \t\n      \n\t\t\n\n\n      \n      Venue\n\n              Imperial Theatre\n      \n              12 King Square South, Saint John NB, E2L 5B8\n      \n              \n          \n            View on Google Maps\n          \n        \n          \n  \n  \n\n\n\n{\n    \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n    \"@type\": \"Event\",\n    \"@id\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/solitary-man-celebrating-the-music-of-neil-diamond/21401ATBPGTQKVRDDCCQRVVVPPKQMSKBM/#event-21401atbpgtqkvrddccqrvvvppkqmskbm\",\n    \"name\": \"Solitary Man: Celebrating the Music of Neil Diamond\",\n    \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/solitary-man-celebrating-the-music-of-neil-diamond/21401ATBPGTQKVRDDCCQRVVVPPKQMSKBM/\",\n    \"eventAttendanceMode\": \"https://schema.org/OfflineEventAttendanceMode\",\n    \"eventStatus\": \"https://schema.org/EventScheduled\",\n    \"location\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Place\",\n        \"name\": \"Imperial Theatre\",\n        \"sameAs\": [\n            \"http://kg.artsdata.ca/resource/K11-193\",\n            \"http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q3527482\"\n        ],\n        \"address\": {\n            \"@type\": \"PostalAddress\",\n            \"streetAddress\": \"12 King Square South\",\n            \"addressLocality\": \"Saint John\",\n            \"postalCode\": \"E2L 5B8\",\n            \"addressRegion\": \"New Brunswick\",\n            \"addressCountry\": {\n                \"@type\": \"Country\",\n                \"name\": \"CA\"\n            }\n        }\n    },\n    \"organizer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Imperial Theatre\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/\"\n    },\n    \"description\": \"$56.25 // TIME WARP PROMOTIONS PRESENTS SOLITARY MAN - CELEBRATING THE MUSIC OF NEIL DIAMOND. Will Chalmers is a multi award winning tribute artist and has been in the music industry for over 30 years. He has been performing his Neil Diamond tribute since 2002 and has also performed tributes to Garth Brooks, Conway Twitty, John Lennon and Elvis. He is also part of the Highwaymen Tribute Forever Highwaymen portraying the role of Waylon Jennings. ◦ Will has traveled with his band all over the USA. Canada and also performed in Mexico, Cayman Islands and Europe. Willʼs natural resemblance to Neil Diamond, his flawless replication of Neilʼs singing voice, combined with his outstanding stage presence has been captivating audiences wherever he goes. The response from Neil fans has been an unbelievable experience. Will is both friendly and personable and people approach him with ease, he is always available to speak to people after the performance and welcomes their comments. ◦ Neil Diamond is a Living Legend and it is with much respect and admiration for the singer songwriter that Will Chalmers tribute is performed. People leave the show with a smile on their face and a song in their hearts. https://www.theneildiamondtributeshow.com/\",\n    \"image\": [\n        \"https://system.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/files/5abebd4c-94bd-4d6e-96fa-a98a252f3c63.jpg\"\n    ],\n    \"startDate\": \"2026-10-10T16:30:00-03:00\",\n    \"offers\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Offer\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatrenewbrunswick.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/website/EventDetails.aspx?EventId=21401ATBPGTQKVRDDCCQRVVVPPKQMSKBM\",\n        \"availability\": \"https://schema.org/InStock\",\n        \"validFrom\": \"2026-10-10T16:30:00-03:00\"\n    },\n    \"performer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Thing\",\n        \"additionalType\": [\n            \"http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Agent\",\n            \"http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Agent\"\n        ],\n        \"name\": \"Solitary Man: Celebrating the Music of Neil Diamond\"\n    }\n}\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t