izarre traditions of Halloween, terrifying costume choices, and the true horror of candy corn. A seasonal special packed with sass, satire, and supernatural wit—because nothing is scarier than eternal damnation…except maybe Spirit Halloween. Created by comedian Mike Delamont and developed into a two-act show with co-director/co-writer Chantelle Delamont, the original production premiered in 2015 at Winnipeg's Pantages Theatre. Mike Delamont is a critically acclaimed performer and three-time Canadian Comedy Award-nominated from Victoria, BC. He has appeared on radio with CBC's Laugh Out Loud, CBC's The Debaters, and SiriusXM's Top Comic. Halifax Comedy Festival, Winnipeg Comedy Festival, and at the World Famous Comedy Store in Los Angeles. Presented by Quatro Entertainment\",\n    \"image\": [\n        \"https://system.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/files/57eb21ef-90de-45a7-b43b-8b1c62687b90.jpg\"\n    ],\n    \"startDate\": \"2026-10-15T16:30:00-03:00\",\n    \"offers\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Offer\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatrenewbrunswick.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/website/EventDetails.aspx?EventId=45401AJDKTHQLVSLBBVQGBPQSVNVKLQMM\",\n        \"availability\": \"https://schema.org/InStock\",\n        \"validFrom\": \"2026-10-15T16:30:00-03:00\"\n    },\n    \"performer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Thing\",\n        \"additionalType\": [\n            \"http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Agent\",\n            \"http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Agent\"\n        ],\n        \"name\": \"God Is A Scottish Drag Queen Halloween Spooktacular\"\n    }\n}\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t"
