        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Advance $35 | Door $40 // BIG SHINY 90s is back by popular demand! This band recreates those nostalgic and iconic Big Shiny Tunes cds we all had in the past. Be transported in time as they cover hits from Bush, Collective Soul, Our Lady Peace, Green Day, Creed and so much more! Advance tickets $35. If not sold out, they will be $40 at the door. Doors open at 8:00PM, the show will begin at 9:00PM."
