        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n          \n        \n      \n    \n\n    Mon Oct 26, 2026 • 7:00pm\n\n  \n          Film\n    \n          Retro Film\n      \n\n  Event length: 91 minutes\n\n      Admission $10.00\n    \n      Ticket prices include all taxes and fees.\n    \n  \n\n\n      \n  \n    Buy tickets\n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n  \n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n    \n      \n                  Retro Film: A Nightmare on Elm Street\n        \n                  \n            Rating: R | Year: 1984 // In Wes Craven's classic slasher film, teenager Nancy Thompson (Heather Langenkamp) and her boyfriend (Johnny Depp) must uncover the dark truth concealed by her parents after she and her friends become targets of the spirit of a serial killer.\n          \n        \n              \n\n      \n  \n    Event Info\n\n          \n        Category: Film      \n    \n          \n        Genre: Retro Film      \n    \n          \n        Event Length: 91 minutes\n      \n    \n      \n  \n  \t\t\n\n\n      \n      Venue\n\n              Imperial Theatre\n      \n              12 King Square South, Saint John NB, E2L 5B8\n      \n              \n          \n            View on Google Maps\n          \n        \n          \n  \n      \n        \n    \n    \n          \n        Event Sponsors\n        \n                                                                                    \n      \n      \n      \n  \n\n\n\n{\n    \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n    \"@type\": \"Event\",\n    \"@id\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/retro-film-a-nightmare-on-elm-street/32001ABCGNLKMHMQDQQTTRQRNTSNGPVMC/#event-32001abcgnlkmhmqdqqttrqrntsngpvmc\",\n    \"name\": \"Retro Film: A Nightmare on Elm Street\",\n    \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/retro-film-a-nightmare-on-elm-street/32001ABCGNLKMHMQDQQTTRQRNTSNGPVMC/\",\n    \"eventAttendanceMode\": \"https://sc