        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "$40.00 // Join us for an evening of short films as The Outdoor Outdoor Film Festival (OOFF) celebrates stories of outdoor playgrounds from around the world. Founded with the mission of sharing natural beauty and adventures in our own backyards, OOFF seeks to bring people together through stories of people living life to their fullest outdoors with special attention to films made in Atlantic Canada."
