    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "$56.25 // TIME WARP PROMOTIONS PRESENTS: HELLS BELLS Since their electrifying inception in 1994 in the heart of Toronto, Hells Bells has soared to become the world’s longest-touring tribute to the legendary AC/DC, lighting up stages across North America with unstoppable passion and excitement. Don’t miss your chance to experience Hells Bells—a tribute that not only honours but revives the spirit of AC/DC. Join us for a night where the music is contagious, and the memories are unforgettable. All Ages! Family friendly! Get ready to rock like never before! https://www.hellsbellscanada.com/"
      }
    ],
