    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Advance $40.00 | Door $50.00 // Coldplay have a worldwide following with over 160 million albums sold. 'The Coldplay Show' is one of the most authentic tributes bringing the sonic and visual performance experience imaginable, featuring the most iconic hits that include Scientist, Adventure of a Lifetime, Sky Full of Stars, Something Just Like This and many more. This show includes high tech 3D visual elements bringing to life the true essence with professional band members who embody all of Coldplay's dynamic stage presence. They have performed thousands of shows and sell out festivals, theatres and live music venues. You don't want to miss this! *Doors open at 7:00PM and the event will begin at 8:00PM"
      }
