        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n          \n        \n      \n    \n\n    Fri Nov 6, 2026 • 8:00pm\n\n  \n          Music\n    \n          Tribute\n      \n\n  Event length: 90 minutes\n\n      Admission $40.00\n    \n      Ticket prices include all taxes and fees.\n    \n  \n\n\n      \n  \n    Buy tickets\n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n  \n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n    \n      \n                  Club Rewind: The Coldplay Show\n        \n                  \n            Advance $40.00 | Door $50.00 // Coldplay have a worldwide following with over 160 million albums sold. 'The Coldplay Show' is one of the most authentic tributes bringing the sonic and visual performance experience imaginable, featuring the most iconic hits that include Scientist, Adventure of a Lifetime, Sky Full of Stars, Something Just Like This and many more. This show includes high tech 3D visual elements bringing to life the true essence with professional band members who embody all of Coldplay's dynamic stage presence. They have performed thousands of shows and sell out festivals, theatres and live music venues. You don't want to miss this! *Doors open at 7:00PM and the event will begin at 8:00PM\n          \n        \n              \n\n      \n  \n    Event Info\n\n          \n        Category: Music      \n    \n          \n        Genre: Tribute      \n    \n          \n        Event Length: 90 minutes\n      \n    \n      \n  \n  \t\t\n\n\n      \n      Venue\n\n              Kent Theatre\n      \n              24 Coburg St, Saint John, NB E2L 3J5\n      \n              \n          \n            View on Google Maps\n          \n        \n          \n  \n  \n\n\n\n{\n    \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n    \"@type\": \"Event\",\n    \"@id\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/club-rewind-the-coldplay-show/41001AMGNGHKLQLCLRMPJKPQBNDVJPHRD/#event-41001amgnghklqlclrmpjkpqbndvjphrd\",\n    \"name\": \"Club Rewind: The Coldplay Show\",\n    \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/club-rewind-the-coldplay-show/41001AMGNGHKLQLCLRMPJKPQBNDVJPHRD/\",\n    \"eventAttendanceMode\": \"https://schema.org/OfflineEventAttendanceMode\",\n    \"eventStatus\": \"https://schema.org/EventScheduled\",\n    \"location\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Place\",\n        \"name\": \"Imperial Theatre\",\n        \"sameAs\": [\n            \"http://kg.artsdata.ca/resource/K11-193\",\n            \"http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q3527482\"\n        ],\n        \"address\": {\n            \"@type\": \"PostalAddress\",\n            \"streetAddress\": \"12 King Square South\",\n            \"addressLocality\": \"Saint John\",\n            \"postalCode\": \"E2L 5B8\",\n            \"addressRegion\": \"New Brunswick\",\n            \"addressCountry\": {\n                \"@type\": \"Country\",\n                \"name\": \"CA\"\n            }\n        }\n    },\n    \"organizer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Imperial Theatre\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/\"\n    },\n    \"description\": \"Advance $40.00 | Door $50.00 // Coldplay have a worldwide following with over 160 million albums sold. 'The Coldplay Show' is one of the most authentic tributes bringing the sonic and visual performance experience imaginable, featuring the most iconic hits that include Scientist, Adventure of a Lifetime, Sky Full of Stars, Something Just Like This and many more. This show includes high tech 3D visual elements bringing to life the true essence with professional band members who embody all of Coldplay's dynamic stage presence. They have performed thousands of shows and sell out festivals, theatres and live music venues. You don't want to miss this! *Doors open at 7:00PM and the event will begin at 8:00PM\",\n    \"image\": [\n        \"https://system.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/files/cc79c88c-99c1-469d-9a85-3e3dce3e9876.jpg\"\n    ],\n    \"startDate\": \"2026-11-06T16:00:00-04:00\",\n    \"offers\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Offer\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatrenewbrunswick.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/website/EventDetails.aspx?EventId=41001AMGNGHKLQLCLRMPJKPQBNDVJPHRD\",\n        \"availability\": \"https://schema.org/InStock\",\n        \"validFrom\": \"2026-11-06T16:00:00-04:00\"\n    },\n    \"performer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Thing\",\n        \"additionalType\": [\n            \"http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Agent\",\n            \"http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Agent\"\n        ],\n        \"name\": \"Club Rewind: The Coldplay Show\"\n    }\n}\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t"
      }
