        "@value": "Leif Vollebekk VIP Add-On"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "$49.00 // Please note that a show ticket is required to participate in the VIP upgrade. Tickets for the show are sold separately. Short Film “Southern Star\" Screening & Conversation: An Exclusive VIP Experience with Leif Vollebekk | Step behind the camera and into the cinematic vision of Leif Vollebekk. Before the music starts, join Leif for an exclusive, intimate screening of his short film, \"Southern Star,\" offering a rare look at how his storytelling translates from sound to screen. Before the doors open to the general public, join Leif for a curated session where he pulls back the curtain on his artistic process. This experience includes: - Exclusive Film Screening: A private viewing of Leif’s short film, \"Southern Star,\" directed by Kaveh Nabatian. The film will take place before the venue doors open to the general public. - Artist Q&A: Leif will take the stage after the credits roll to discuss the film’s creation, its connection to his music, and to answer a few of your questions. - Photo Opportunity: Commemorate the evening with an official photo alongside Leif. - First Access to Merch: Skip the lines with a head start on shopping tour-exclusive merchandise. - Early entry into the venue"
      }
    ],
