        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n          \n        \n      \n    \n\n    Tue Nov 17, 2026 • 6:00pm\n\n  \n          Other\n    \n          Screening\n      \n\n  Event length: 60 minutes\n\n      Admission $49.00\n    \n      Ticket prices include all taxes and fees.\n    \n  \n\n\n      \n  \n    Buy tickets\n  \n\n      \n      IT Member Event\n    \n  \n  \n  \n  \n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n    \n      \n                  Leif Vollebekk VIP Add-On\n        \n                  \n            Please note that a show ticket is required to participate in the VIP upgrade. Tickets for the show are sold separately. \n Short Film “Southern Star\" Screening & Conversation: An Exclusive VIP Experience with Leif Vollebekk |\nStep behind the camera and into the cinematic vision of Leif Vollebekk. Before the music starts, join Leif for an exclusive, intimate screening of his short film, \"Southern Star,\"  offering a rare look at how his storytelling translates from sound to screen. Before the doors open to the general public, join Leif for a curated session where he pulls back the curtain on his artistic process. This experience includes:\n- Exclusive Film Screening: A private viewing of Leif’s short film, \"Southern Star,\" directed by Kaveh Nabatian. The film will take place before the venue doors open to the general public.\n- Artist Q&A: Leif will take the stage after the credits roll to discuss the film’s creation, its connection to his music, and to answer a few of your questions.\n- Photo Opportunity: Commemorate the evening with an official photo alongside Leif.\n- First Access to Merch: Skip the lines with a head start on shopping tour-exclusive merchandise.\n- Early entry into the venue\n          \n        \n              \n\n      \n  \n    Event Info\n\n          \n        Category: Other      \n    \n          \n        Genre: Screening      \n    \n          \n        Event Length: 60 minutes\n      \n    \n      \n  \n  \t\t\n\n\n      \n      Venue\n\n              Imperial Theatre\n      \n              12 King Square South, Saint John NB, E2L 5B8\n      \n              \n          \n            View on Google Maps\n          \n        \n          \n  \n      \n        \n    \n    \n          \n        Event Sponsor\n        \n                                        \n      \n      \n      \n  \n\n\n\n{\n    \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n    \"@type\": \"Event\",\n    \"@id\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/leif-vollebekk-vip-add-on/41601AVNPVJKVCKMRJHHMRKVNNMTGJHSV/#event-41601avnpvjkvckmrjhhmrkvnnmtgjhsv\",\n    \"name\": \"Leif Vollebekk VIP Add-On\",\n    \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/leif-vollebekk-vip-add-on/41601AVNPVJKVCKMRJHHMRKVNNMTGJHSV/\",\n    \"eventAttendanceMode\": \"https://schema.org/OfflineEventAttendanceMode\",\n    \"eventStatus\": \"https://schema.org/EventScheduled\",\n    \"location\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Place\",\n        \"name\": \"Imperial Theatre\",\n        \"sameAs\": [\n            \"http://kg.artsdata.ca/resource/K11-193\",\n            \"http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q3527482\"\n        ],\n        \"address\": {\n            \"@type\": \"PostalAddress\",\n            \"streetAddress\": \"12 King Square South\",\n            \"addressLocality\": \"Saint John\",\n            \"postalCode\": \"E2L 5B8\",\n            \"addressRegion\": \"New Brunswick\",\n            \"addressCountry\": {\n                \"@type\": \"Country\",\n                \"name\": \"CA\"\n            }\n        }\n    },\n    \"organizer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Imperial Theatre\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/\"\n    },\n    \"description\": \"$49.00 // Please note that a show ticket is required to participate in the VIP upgrade. Tickets for the show are sold separately. Short Film “Southern Star\\\" Screening & Conversation: An Exclusive VIP Experience with Leif Vollebekk | Step behind the camera and into the cinematic vision of Leif Vollebekk. Before the music starts, join Leif for an exclusive, intimate screening of his short film, \\\"Southern Star,\\\" offering a rare look at how his storytelling translates from sound to screen. Before the doors open to the general public, join Leif for a curated session where he pulls back the curtain on his artistic process. This experience includes: - Exclusive Film Screening: A private viewing of Leif’s short film, \\\"Southern Star,\\\" directed by Kaveh Nabatian. The film will take place before the venue doors open to the general public. - Artist Q&A: Leif will take the stage after the credits roll to discuss the film’s creation, its connection to his music, and to answer a few of your questions. - Photo Opportunity: Commemorate the evening with an official photo alongside Leif. - First Access to Merch: Skip the lines with a head start on shopping tour-exclusive merchandise. - Early entry into the venue\",\n    \"image\": [\n        \"https://system.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/files/e9c14ea8-ab6a-47a2-a1a2-ee6f5f595156.jpg\"\n    ],\n    \"startDate\": \"2026-11-17T14:00:00-04:00\",\n    \"offers\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Offer\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatrenewbrunswick.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/website/EventDetails.aspx?EventId=41601AVNPVJKVCKMRJHHMRKVNNMTGJHSV\",\n        \"availability\": \"https://schema.org/InStock\",\n        \"validFrom\": \"2026-11-17T14:00:00-04:00\"\n    },\n    \"performer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Thing\",\n        \"additionalType\": [\n            \"http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Agent\",\n            \"http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Agent\"\n        ],\n        \"name\": \"Leif Vollebekk VIP Add-On\"\n    }\n}\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t"
