        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n          \n        \n      \n    \n\n    Tue Nov 17, 2026 • 7:30pm\n\n  \n          Music\n    \n          Rock\n      \n\n  Event length: 90 minutes\n\n      Admission $50.00\n    \n      Ticket prices include all taxes and fees.\n    \n  \n\n\n      \n  \n    Buy tickets\n  \n\n      \n      IT Member Event\n    \n  \n  \n  \n  \n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n    \n      \n                  Leif Vollebekk\n        \n                  \n            $50  Regular || $45 Member ||\nMontreal-based crooner Leif Vollebekk creates an intimate, emotionally rich concert experience where soulful melodies and heartfelt lyrics take center stage. With his evocative voice and fluid piano or guitar work, Vollebekk creates a dreamy, immersive atmosphere that feels both raw and deeply personal to listeners. His performances blend folk, indie, and jazz influences, captivating the audience with spontaneous improvisations and stories behind the songs. Whether in a small venue or a larger space, crowds are captivated by the warmth and genuineness of seeing Leif perform. \n          \n        \n              \n\n      \n  \n    Event Info\n\n          \n        Category: Music      \n    \n          \n        Genre: Rock      \n    \n          \n        Event Length: 90 minutes\n      \n    \n      \n  \n  \t\t\n\n\n      \n      Venue\n\n              Imperial Theatre\n      \n              12 King Square South, Saint John NB, E2L 5B8\n      \n              \n          \n            View on Google Maps\n          \n        \n          \n  \n      \n        \n    \n    \n          \n        Event Sponsor\n        \n                                        \n      \n      \n      \n  \n\n\n\n{\n    \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n    \"@type\": \"Event\",\n    \"@id\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/leif-vollebekk/38002ASPBCCVSQCHGKJKKGNQPKLLTCLSB/#event-38002aspbccvsqchgkjkkgnqpklltclsb\",\n    \"name\": \"Leif Vollebekk\",\n    \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/leif-vollebekk/38002ASPBCCVSQCHGKJKKGNQPKLLTCLSB/\",\n    \"eventAttendanceMode\": \"https://schema.org/OfflineEventAttendanceMode\",\n    \"eventStatus\": \"https://schema.org/EventScheduled\",\n    \"location\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Place\",\n        \"name\": \"Imperial Theatre\",\n        \"sameAs\": [\n            \"http://kg.artsdata.ca/resource/K11-193\",\n            \"http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q3527482\"\n        ],\n        \"address\": {\n            \"@type\": \"PostalAddress\",\n            \"streetAddress\": \"12 King Square South\",\n            \"addressLocality\": \"Saint John\",\n            \"postalCode\": \"E2L 5B8\",\n            \"addressRegion\": \"New Brunswick\",\n            \"addressCountry\": {\n                \"@type\": \"Country\",\n                \"name\": \"CA\"\n            }\n        }\n    },\n    \"organizer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Imperial Theatre\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/\"\n    },\n    \"description\": \"$50 Regular || $45 Member || Montreal-based crooner Leif Vollebekk creates an intimate, emotionally rich concert experience where soulful melodies and heartfelt lyrics take center stage. With his evocative voice and fluid piano or guitar work, Vollebekk creates a dreamy, immersive atmosphere that feels both raw and deeply personal to listeners. His performances blend folk, indie, and jazz influences, captivating the audience with spontaneous improvisations and stories behind the songs. Whether in a small venue or a larger space, crowds are captivated by the warmth and genuineness of seeing Leif perform.\",\n    \"image\": [\n        \"https://system.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/files/f22fe945-4da4-4d34-8897-f216b9e64669.jpg\"\n    ],\n    \"startDate\": \"2026-11-17T15:30:00-04:00\",\n    \"offers\": {\