    "https://schema.org/mainContentOfPage": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n          \n        \n      \n    \n\n    Sat Nov 21, 2026 • 8:00pm\n\n  \n          Comedy\n    \n          Presentation\n      \n\n  Event length: 100 minutes\n\n      Admission $66.25 | Admission $61.25 | Admission $56.25\n    \n      Ticket prices include all taxes and fees.\n    \n  \n\n\n      \n  \n    Buy tickets\n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n  \n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n    \n      \n                  HYPROV: Improv Under Hypnosis\n        \n                  \n            Advance P1 $66.25 | P2 $61.25 | P3 $56.25 / Day of P1 $71.25 | P2 $66.25 | P3 $61.25 //\nHilarious. Unpredictable. Unlike anything you’ve ever seen.\nFrom improv legend Colin Mochrie (Whose Line Is It Anyway?) and world-renowned hypnotist Asad Mecci, HYPROV is a boundary-breaking comedy experience that fuses hypnosis and improvisation into one electrifying show.\n The New York Times raves, “The audience erupted in laughter … it killed.”\nTime Out New York calls it “hilarious and fascinating.”\nThe Wall Street Journal praises it as “catnip for those who relish spontaneity.”\nHow It Works: Twenty audience volunteers take the stage — completely voluntarily. Within minutes, Asad Mecci guides them into a state of fearless creativity. The most receptive “Hyprovisors” then join Colin Mochrie to perform a completely improvised comedy show — while hypnotized.\nNo script. No safety net. Just raw imagination and real laughter unfolding live.  \nWith improvised music driving the rhythm, every performance is a one-of-a-kind high-wire act of comedy, chaos, and connection.\nHYPROV isn’t just a show — it’s part mind experiment, part comedy lab, and 100 percent entertainment. No two nights are ever the same.\nWhether you’re a Whose Line fan, a live-comedy junkie, or simply chasing an unforgettable night out, HYPROV delivers.\nPost-show Meet & Greet available, sold separately: https://hyprov.com/store/p/hyprov-meet-and-greet-with-colin-mochrie-and-asad-mecci\n          \n        \n              \n\n      \n  \n    Event Info\n\n          \n        Category: Comedy      \n    \n          \n        Genre: Presentation      \n    \n          \n        Event Length: 100 minutes\n      \n    \n      \n  \n  \t\t\n\n\n      \n      Venue\n\n              Imperial Theatre\n      \n              12 King Square South, Saint John NB, E2L 5B8\n      \n              \n          \n            View on Google Maps\n          \n        \n          \n  \n  \n\n\n\n{\n    \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n    \"@type\": \"Event\",\n    \"@id\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/hyprov-improv-under-hypnosis/35601ALVJGKRTKBQLPHGRMJPNQQKSPRPT/#event-35601alvjgkrtkbqlphgrmjpnqqksprpt\",\n    \"name\": \"HYPROV: Improv Under Hypnosis\",\n    \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/hyprov-improv-under-hypnosis/35601ALVJGKRTKBQLPHGRMJPNQQKSPRPT/\",\n    \"eventAttendanceMode\": \"https://schema.org/OfflineEventAttendanceMode\",\n    \"eventStatus\": \"https://schema.org/EventScheduled\",\n    \"location\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Place\",\n        \"name\": \"Imperial Theatre\",\n        \"sameAs\": [\n            \"http://kg.artsdata.ca/resource/K11-193\",\n            \"http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q3527482\"\n        ],\n        \"address\": {\n            \"@type\": \"PostalAddress\",\n            \"streetAddress\": \"12 King Square South\",\n            \"addressLocality\": \"Saint John\",\n            \"postalCode\": \"E2L 5B8\",\n            \"addressRegion\": \"New Brunswick\",\n            \"addressCountry\": {\n                \"@type\": \"Country\",\n                \"name\": \"CA\"\n            }\n        }\n    },\n    \"organizer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Imperial Theatre\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/\"\n    },\n    \"description\": \"Advance P1 $66.25 | P2 $61.25 | P3 $56.25 / Day of P1 $71.25 | P2 $66.25 | P3 $61.25 // Hilarious. Unpredictable. Unlike anything you’ve ever seen. From improv legend Colin Mochrie (Whose Line Is It Anyway?) and world-renowned hypnotist Asad Mecci, HYPROV is a boundary-breaking comedy experience that fuses hypnosis and improvisation into one electrifying show. The New York Times raves, “The audience erupted in laughter … it killed.” Time Out New York calls it “hilarious and fascinating.” The Wall Street Journal praises it as “catnip for those who relish spontaneity.” How It Works: Twenty audience volunteers take the stage — completely voluntarily. Within minutes, Asad Mecci guides them into a state of fearless creativity. The most receptive “Hyprovisors” then join Colin Mochrie to perform a completely improvised comedy show — while hypnotized. No script. No safety net. Just raw imagination and real laughter unfolding live. With improvised music driving the rhythm, every performance is a one-of-a-kind high-wire act of comedy, chaos, and connection. HYPROV isn’t just a show — it’s part mind experiment, part comedy lab, and 100 percent entertainment. No two nights are ever the same. Whether you’re a Whose Line fan, a live-comedy junkie, or simply chasing an unforgettable night out, HYPROV delivers. Post-show Meet & Greet available, sold separately: https://hyprov.com/store/p/hyprov-meet-and-greet-with-colin-mochrie-and-asad-mecci\",\n    \"image\": [\n        \"https://system.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/files/8470acd2-32a2-446f-8cd6-87e1f76cc836.jpg\"\n    ],\n    \"startDate\": \"2026-11-21T16:00:00-04:00\",\n    \"offers\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Offer\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatrenewbrunswick.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/website/EventDetails.aspx?EventId=35601ALVJGKRTKBQLPHGRMJPNQQKSPRPT\",\n        \"availability\": \"https://schema.org/InStock\",\n        \"validFrom\": \"2026-11-21T16:00:00-04:00\"\n    },\n    \"performer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Thing\"