ts now to avoid the holiday rush! These special shows are just for live audiences and aren’t recorded for broadcast.\",\n    \"image\": [\n        \"https://system.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/files/dacd7282-0912-47f1-8e30-279244fc48ae.jpg\"\n    ],\n    \"startDate\": \"2026-12-14T15:30:00-04:00\",\n    \"offers\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Offer\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatrenewbrunswick.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/website/EventDetails.aspx?EventId=38402AHVQSHJNGJDCVCGTLMGCKSVGPKPG\",\n        \"availability\": \"https://schema.org/InStock\",\n        \"validFrom\": \"2026-12-14T15:30:00-04:00\"\n    },\n    \"performer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Thing\",\n        \"additionalType\": [\n            \"http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Agent\",\n            \"http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Agent\"\n        ],\n        \"name\": \"The Debaters Live On Tour: 20th Anniversary Holiday Special\"\n    }\n}\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t"
