    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Matt Dusk: A Very Sinatra Christmas"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Admission $75.25 | Platinum-selling crooner and five-time Juno Award nominee Matt Dusk returns to the spotlight this holiday season with A Very Sinatra Christmas, a festive and unforgettable concert experience coming to 22 cities from coast to coast. Backed by a powerhouse big band, Dusk will transport audiences to the golden age of swing, blending timeless holiday classics with the unforgettable style of the one-and- only Frank Sinatra. From “It’s the Most Wonderful Time of the Year” to “The Christmas Song”, A Very Sinatra Christmas is brimming with nostalgia, glamour, and holiday spirit - perfect for fans of classic music and unforgettable live entertainment."
      }
    ],
