      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n          \n        \n      \n    \n\n    Mon Jan 18, 2027 • 7:30pm\n\n  \n          Theatre\n    \n          Play\n      \n\n  Event length: 80 minutes\n\n      Admission $60.00\n    \n      Ticket prices include all taxes and fees.\n    \n  \n\n\n      \n  \n    Buy tickets\n  \n\n      \n      IT Member Event\n    \n  \n  \n  \n  \n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n    \n      \n                  Little Red Warrior & His Lawyer\n        \n                  \n            $60 Regular || $55 Member ||\nA wickedly funny trickster land claim fable by Kevin Loring In this wickedly funny satire about power, politics, and procreation, Little Red Warrior is the last remaining member of the Little Red Warrior First Nation. One day he discovers the development company Smith, Smyth and Goldsmithe has begun construction on his ancestral lands. In a fit of rage, he attacks one of their engineers, gets arrested and lands in jail. After Larry, his court-appointed lawyer bails him out, he has nowhere to live. Much to the dismay of his wife Desdemona, Larry invites Little Red Warrior to stay. But when you invite a coyote into your coop, he might just walk away with all the chickens.\n          \n        \n              \n\n      \n  \n    Event Info\n\n          \n        Category: Theatre      \n    \n          \n        Genre: Play      \n    \n          \n        Event Length: 80 minutes\n      \n    \n      \n  \n  \t\t\n\n\n      \n      Venue\n\n              Imperial Theatre\n      \n              12 King Square South, Saint John NB, E2L 5B8\n      \n              \n          \n            View on Google Maps\n          \n        \n          \n  \n  \n\n\n\n{\n    \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n    \"@type\": \"Event\",\n    \"@id\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/little-red-warrior-his-lawyer/38403AMSDMRGHRBJSTVPHSKKVBVQDRCDC/#event-38403amsdmrghrbjstvphskkvbvqdrcdc\",\n    \"name\": \"Little Red Warrior & His Lawyer\",\n    \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/little-red-warrior-his-lawyer/38403AMSDMRGHRBJSTVPHSKKVBVQDRCDC/\",\n    \"eventAttendanceMode\": \"https://schema.org/OfflineEventAttendanceMode\",\n    \"eventStatus\": \"https://schema.org/EventScheduled\",\n    \"location\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Place\",\n        \"name\": \"Imperial Theatre\",\n        \"sameAs\": [\n            \"http://kg.artsdata.ca/resource/K11-193\",\n            \"http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q3527482\"\n        ],\n        \"address\": {\n            \"@type\": \"PostalAddress\",\n            \"streetAddress\": \"12 King Square South\",\n            \"addressLocality\": \"Saint John\",\n            \"postalCode\": \"E2L 5B8\",\n            \"addressRegion\": \"New Brunswick\",\n            \"addressCountry\": {\n                \"@type\": \"Country\",\n                \"name\": \"CA\"\n            }\n        }\n    },\n    \"organizer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Imperial Theatre\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/\"\n    },\n    \"description\": \"$60 Regular || $55 Member || A wickedly funny trickster land claim fable by Kevin Loring In this wickedly funny satire about power, politics, and procreation, Little Red Warrior is the last remaining member of the Little Red Warrior First Nation. One day he discovers the development company Smith, Smyth and Goldsmithe has begun construction on his ancestral lands. In a fit of rage, he attacks one of their engineers, gets arrested and lands in jail. After Larry, his court-appointed lawyer bails him out, he has nowhere to live. Much to the dismay of his wife Desdemona, Larry invites Little Red Warrior to stay. But when you invite a coyote into your coop, he might just walk away with all the chickens.\",\n    \"image\": [\n        \"https://system.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/files/36e1c07c-5551-4f25-89b0-41913d3ebe03.jpg\"\n    ],\n    \"startDate\": \"2027-01-18T15:30:00-04:00\",\n    \"offers\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Offer\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatrenewbrunswick.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/website/EventDetails.aspx?EventId=38403AMSDMRGHRBJSTVPHSKKVBVQDRCDC\",\n        \"availability\": \"https://schema.org/InStock\",\n        \"validFrom\": \"2027-01-18T15:30:00-04:00\"\n    },\n    \"performer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Thing\",\n        \"additionalType\": [\n            \"http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Agent\",\n            \"http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Agent\"\n        ],\n        \"name\": \"Little Red Warrior & His Lawyer\"\n    }\n}\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t"
