        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n          \n        \n      \n    \n\n    Sat Feb 6, 2027 • 7:30pm\n\n  \n          Music\n    \n          Tribute\n      \n\n  Event length: 110 minutes\n\n      Admission $67.00 | Admission $63.00 | Admission $59.00\n    \n      Ticket prices include all taxes and fees.\n    \n  \n\n\n      \n  \n    Buy tickets\n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n  \n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n    \n      \n                  The Highwaymen: Great Outlaws Tribute\n        \n                  \n            A Seating $67.00 | B Seating $63.00 | C Seating $59.00 //\nVaughnCo Entertainment is proud to present\nHighwaymen Show – Great Outlaws Tribute\n \nIn 1984, Johnny Cash invited Willie Nelson, Waylon Jennings and Kris Kristofferson to play on his Johnny Cash Christmas TV Special that was filmed in Switzerland.  When they got back to the hotel, they started jamming and hanging out and that was how the Highwaymen came to be. \nThe Highwaymen Show pays tribute to the great American Outlaws of Country Music - Johnny Cash, Willie Nelson, Waylon Jennings and Kris Kristofferson. The Show covers all of the greatest hits including “Mama Don't Let Your Babies Grow up to be Cowboys”, “Always on My Mind”, “Me and Bobby McGee” and “Folsom Prison Blues.”\nDon’t miss this trip down memory lane with the look and sound of these iconic superstars: The entire show will feel like an encore! //\nSee more at https://vimeo.com/1088441184 or\nhttps://youtu.be/5svMBQmIyiQ\n          \n        \n              \n\n      \n  \n    Event Info\n\n          \n        Category: Music      \n    \n          \n        Genre: Tribute      \n    \n          \n        Event Length: 110 minutes\n      \n    \n      \n  \n  \t\t\n\n\n      \n      Venue\n\n              Imperial Theatre\n      \n              12 King Square South, Saint John NB, E2L 5B8\n      \n              \n          \n            View on Google Maps\n          \n        \n          \n  \n  \n\n\n\n{\n    \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n    \"@type\": \"Event\",\n    \"@id\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/the-highwaymen-great-outlaws-tribute/28201ANLRQMDQPKBCRBQJSVDBPMCHQKNS/#event-28201anlrqmdqpkbcrbqjsvdbpmchqkns\",\n    \"name\": \"The Highwaymen: Great Outlaws Tribute\",\n    \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/the-highwaymen-great-outlaws-tribute/28201ANLRQMDQPKBCRBQJSVDBPMCHQKNS/\",\n    \"eventAttendanceMode\": \"https://schema.org/OfflineEventAttendanceMode\",\n    \"eventStatus\": \"https://schema.org/EventScheduled\",\n    \"location\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Place\",\n        \"name\": \"Imperial Theatre\",\n        \"sameAs\": [\n            \"http://kg.artsdata.ca/resource/K11-193\",\n            \"http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q3527482\"\n        ],\n        \"address\": {\n            \"@type\": \"PostalAddress\",\n            \"streetAddress\": \"12 King Square South\",\n            \"addressLocality\": \"Saint John\",\n            \"postalCode\": \"E2L 5B8\",\n            \"addressRegion\": \"New Brunswick\",\n            \"addressCountry\": {\n                \"@type\": \"Country\",\n                \"name\": \"CA\"\n            }\n        }\n    },\n    \"organizer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Imperial Theatre\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/\"\n    },\n    \"description\": \"A Seating $67.00 | B Seating $63.00 | C Seating $59.00 // VaughnCo Entertainment is proud to present Highwaymen Show – Great Outlaws Tribute   In 1984, Johnny Cash invited Willie Nelson, Waylon Jennings and Kris Kristofferson to play on his Johnny Cash Christmas TV Special that was filmed in Switzerland.  When they got back to the hotel, they started jamming and hanging out and that was how the Highwaymen came to be.  The Highwaymen Show pays tribute to the great American Outlaws of Country Music - Johnny Cash, Willie Nelson, Waylon Jennings and Kris Kristofferson. The Show covers all of the greatest hits including “Mama Don't Let Your Babies Grow up to be Cowboys”, “Always on My Mind”, “Me and Bobby McGee” and “Folsom Prison Blues.” Don’t miss this trip down memory lane with the look and sound of these iconic superstars: The entire show will feel like an encore! // See more at https://vimeo.com/1088441184 or https://youtu.be/5svMBQmIyiQ\",\n    \"image\": [\n        \"https://system.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/files/76e9d605-69df-447b-8b0a-b10d5d03f7e2.jpg\"\n    ],\n    \"startDate\": \"2027-02-06T15:30:00-04:00\",\n    \"offers\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Offer\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatrenewbrunswick.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/website/EventDetails.aspx?EventId=28201ANLRQMDQPKBCRBQJSVDBPMCHQKNS\",\n        \"availability\": \"https://schema.org/InStock\",\n        \"validFrom\": \"2027-02-06T15:30:00-04:00\"\n    },\n    \"performer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Thing\",\n        \"additionalType\": [\n            \"http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Agent\",\n            \"http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Agent\"\n        ],\n        \"name\": \"The Highwaymen: Great Outlaws Tribute\"\n    }\n}\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t"
