tofferson. The Show covers all of the greatest hits including “Mama Don't Let Your Babies Grow up to be Cowboys”, “Always on My Mind”, “Me and Bobby McGee” and “Folsom Prison Blues.” Don’t miss this trip down memory lane with the look and sound of these iconic superstars: The entire show will feel like an encore! // See more at https://vimeo.com/1088441184 or https://youtu.be/5svMBQmIyiQ\",\n    \"image\": [\n        \"https://system.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/files/76e9d605-69df-447b-8b0a-b10d5d03f7e2.jpg\"\n    ],\n    \"startDate\": \"2027-02-06T15:30:00-04:00\",\n    \"offers\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Offer\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatrenewbrunswick.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/website/EventDetails.aspx?EventId=28201ANLRQMDQPKBCRBQJSVDBPMCHQKNS\",\n        \"availability\": \"https://schema.org/InStock\",\n        \"validFrom\": \"2027-02-06T15:30:00-04:00\"\n    },\n    \"performer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Thing\",\n        \"additionalType\": [\n            \"http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Agent\",\n            \"http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Agent\"\n        ],\n        \"name\": \"The Highwaymen: Great Outlaws Tribute\"\n    }\n}\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t"
