        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n          \n        \n      \n    \n\n    Fri Feb 12, 2027 • 7:00pm\n\n  \n          Film\n    \n          Retro Film\n      \n\n  Event length: 109 minutes\n\n      Admission $10.00\n    \n      Ticket prices include all taxes and fees.\n    \n  \n\n\n      \n  \n    Buy tickets\n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n  \n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n    \n      \n                  Retro Film: The Devil Wears Prada\n        \n                  \n            Rating: PG-13 | Year: 2006 // Aspiring journalist Andrea \"Andy\" Sachs (Anne Hathaway) has recently graduated from journalism school. Despite her lack of knowledge of the fashion industry, she is hired as a junior personal assistant to Miranda Priestly (Meryl Streep), a job that becomes nightmarish as she struggles to keep up with her boss's grueling schedule and demeaning demands\n          \n        \n              \n\n      \n  \n    Event Info\n\n          \n        Category: Film      \n    \n          \n        Genre: Retro Film      \n    \n          \n        Event Length: 109 minutes\n      \n    \n      \n  \n  \t\t\n\n\n      \n      Venue\n\n              Imperial Theatre\n      \n              12 King Square South, Saint John NB, E2L 5B8\n      \n              \n          \n            View on Google Maps\n          \n        \n          \n  \n      \n        \n    \n    \n          \n        Event Sponsors\n        \n                                                              \n      \n      \n      \n  \n\n\n\n{\n    \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n    \"@type\": \"Event\",\n    \"@id\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/retro-film-the-devil-wears-prada/32602ACHLMHLSDRSBMCVLHTSHSHDVRQTM/#event-32602achlmhlsdrsbmcvlhtshshdvrqtm\",\n    \"name\": \"Retro Film: The Devil Wears Prada\",\n    \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/retro-film-the-devil-wears-prada/