        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "$37.50 Regular || $32.50 Member || 65 million years ago, dinosaurs ruled the earth... 30 years ago, a movie about dinosaurs ruled the box office... This year, you are invited to… Hold On To Your Butts Following its critically acclaimed West End and Off-Broadway debuts, the smash hit show goes on tour! Two actors and a Foley artist perform a live, shot-for-shot parody of the greatest dinosaur film of all time. A wildly inventive tour-de-force of comedy, physical theatre and live Foley. ★★★★★ “A non-stop laugh fest” (Theatre Weekly) ★★★★★ “A chaotic masterpiece” (Stage to Page) ★★★★ “A funny, head-spinning Jurassic Park parody” (The Times) CRITIC’S PICK “Painfully funny ... made us cry actual tears of laughter ... a pure joy from start to finish” (Time Out) “It’s the hit of the Fringe” (Scottish Daily Mail)"
