        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n          \n        \n      \n    \n\n    Thu Feb 18, 2027 • 7:30pm\n\n  \n          Comedy\n    \n          Play\n      \n\n  Event length: 55 minutes\n\n      Admission $37.50\n    \n      Ticket prices include all taxes and fees.\n    \n  \n\n\n      \n  \n    Buy tickets\n  \n\n      \n      IT Member Event\n    \n  \n  \n  \n  \n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n    \n      \n                  Hold onto Your Butts\n        \n                  \n            $37.50 Regular || $32.50 Member ||\n65 million years ago, dinosaurs ruled the earth...\n30 years ago, a movie about dinosaurs ruled the box office...\nThis year, you are invited to… \nHold On To Your Butts\nFollowing its critically acclaimed West End and Off-Broadway debuts, the smash hit show goes on tour!\nTwo actors and a Foley artist perform a live, shot-for-shot parody of the greatest dinosaur film of all time. A wildly inventive tour-de-force of comedy, physical theatre and live Foley.\n★★★★★ “A non-stop laugh fest” (Theatre Weekly)\n★★★★★ “A chaotic masterpiece” (Stage to Page)\n★★★★ “A funny, head-spinning Jurassic Park parody” (The Times)\nCRITIC’S PICK “Painfully funny ... made us cry actual tears of laughter ... a pure joy from start to finish” (Time Out)\n“It’s the hit of the Fringe” (Scottish Daily Mail)\n          \n        \n              \n\n      \n  \n    Event Info\n\n          \n        Category: Comedy      \n    \n          \n        Genre: Play      \n    \n          \n        Event Length: 55 minutes\n      \n    \n      \n  \n  \t\t\n\n\n      \n      Venue\n\n              Imperial Theatre\n      \n              12 King Square South, Saint John NB, E2L 5B8\n      \n              \n          \n            View on Google Maps\n          \n        \n          \n  \n      \n        \n    \n    \n          \n        Event Sponsor\n        \n         