rk parody” (The Times) CRITIC’S PICK “Painfully funny ... made us cry actual tears of laughter ... a pure joy from start to finish” (Time Out) “It’s the hit of the Fringe” (Scottish Daily Mail)\",\n    \"image\": [\n        \"https://system.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/files/31473f7c-221e-4baa-bb8f-ee4d29e76ba5.jpg\"\n    ],\n    \"startDate\": \"2027-02-18T15:30:00-04:00\",\n    \"offers\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Offer\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatrenewbrunswick.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/website/EventDetails.aspx?EventId=38004ASDVJGHHHJTBCMLJTDHCSKRQRRDC\",\n        \"availability\": \"https://schema.org/InStock\",\n        \"validFrom\": \"2027-02-18T15:30:00-04:00\"\n    },\n    \"performer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Thing\",\n        \"additionalType\": [\n            \"http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Agent\",\n            \"http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Agent\"\n        ],\n        \"name\": \"Hold onto Your Butts\"\n    }\n}\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t"
