    "https://schema.org/mainContentOfPage": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n          \n        \n      \n    \n\n    Fri Feb 26, 2027 • 6:00pm\n\n  \n          Theatre\n    \n          Play\n      \n\n  Event length: 55 minutes\n\n      Adult $35.00 | Youth $20.00\n    \n      Ticket prices include all taxes and fees.\n    \n  \n\n\n      \n  \n    Buy tickets\n  \n\n      \n      IT Member Event\n    \n  \n  \n  \n  \n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n    \n      \n                  Over There / Là-Bas L'Aubergine Theatre\n        \n                  \n            $35 Adult || $30 Member || $20 Youth || Family $100\n\"Là-bas is a clown show produced by L'Aubergine, featuring a trio of inseparable friends on a journey toward a better future. The production centers on themes of mutual aid, solidarity, and fraternal friendship, portrayed through the characters' comical and wacky adventures.Production Team and Creatives\nDirector & Original Idea: Véronika Makdissi-Warren\nAssistant Director: Mélissa Bouchard\nPerformers: Miguel Fontaine, Amélie Gadbois, and Jocelyn Paré\nSet Design and Lighting: Christian Fontaine\nCostumes: Julie Morel\nMusic: Stéphane Caron\"\n          \n        \n              \n\n      \n  \n    Event Info\n\n          \n        Category: Theatre      \n    \n          \n        Genre: Play      \n    \n          \n        Event Length: 55 minutes\n      \n    \n      \n  \n  \t\t\n\n\n      \n      Venue\n\n              Imperial Theatre\n      \n              12 King Square South, Saint John NB, E2L 5B8\n      \n              \n          \n            View on Google Maps\n          \n        \n          \n  \n      \n        \n    \n    \n          \n        Event Sponsor\n        \n                                        \n      \n      \n      \n  \n\n\n\n{\n    \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n    \"@type\": \"Event\",\n    \"@id\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/over-there-la-bas-laubergine-theatre/41801AVTMRHQTMCCLMJSHHVVQTNHJPGQB/#event-41801avtmrhqtmcclmjshhvvqtnhjpgqb\",\n    \"name\": \"Over There / Là-Bas L'Aubergine Theatre\",\n    \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/over-there-la-bas-laubergine-theatre/41801AVTMRHQTMCCLMJSHHVVQTNHJPGQB/\",\n    \"eventAttendanceMode\": \"https://schema.org/OfflineEventAttendanceMode\",\n    \"eventStatus\": \"https://schema.org/EventScheduled\",\n    \"location\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Place\",\n        \"name\": \"Imperial Theatre\",\n        \"sameAs\": [\n            \"http://kg.artsdata.ca/resource/K11-193\",\n            \"http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q3527482\"\n        ],\n        \"address\": {\n            \"@type\": \"PostalAddress\",\n            \"streetAddress\": \"12 King Square South\",\n            \"addressLocality\": \"Saint John\",\n            \"postalCode\": \"E2L 5B8\",\n            \"addressRegion\": \"New Brunswick\",\n            \"addressCountry\": {\n                \"@type\": \"Country\",\n                \"name\": \"CA\"\n            }\n        }\n    },\n    \"organizer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Imperial Theatre\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/\"\n    },\n    \"description\": \"$35 Adult || $30 Member || $20 Youth || Family $100 \\\"Là-bas is a clown show produced by L'Aubergine, featuring a trio of inseparable friends on a journey toward a better future. The production centers on themes of mutual aid, solidarity, and fraternal friendship, portrayed through the characters' comical and wacky adventures.Production Team and Creatives Director & Original Idea: Véronika Makdissi-Warren Assistant Director: Mélissa Bouchard Performers: Miguel Fontaine, Amélie Gadbois, and Jocelyn Paré Set Design and Lighting: Christian Fontaine Costumes: Julie Morel Music: Stéphane Caron\\\"\",\n    \"image\": [\n        \"https://system.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/files/6b59f188-d5ad-434e-9ece-5f647a