    "https://schema.org/mainContentOfPage": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n          \n        \n      \n    \n\n    Wed Mar 10, 2027 • 7:30pm\n\n  \n          Music\n    \n          Tribute\n      \n\n  Event length: 110 minutes\n\n      Admission $69.00 | Admission $64.00 | Admission $59.00\n    \n      Ticket prices include all taxes and fees.\n    \n  \n\n\n      \n  \n    Buy tickets\n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n  \n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n    \n      \n                  Hotel California: The Original Eagles Tribute\n        \n                  \n            A Seating $69.00 | B Seating $64.00 | C Seating $59.00 //\nVaughnCo Entertainment is proud to present\n \nHotel California - The Original Eagles Tribute\nWhen The Eagles stopped to catch their breath a few decades ago, having sold over 100 million records, collected six Grammys, and enjoyed six #1 albums, Hotel California began a pioneering journey through their history-making music that has taken them around the globe and thrilled hundreds of thousands of Eagles fans. Hotel California toured relentlessly from the 80’s straight through to today, setting the standard for world-class tribute productions as they went, and sharing stages with the likes of The Doobie Bros., Lynyrd Skynyrd, Gretchen Wilson, REO Speedwagon, and many more. From Japan to Dubai, Toronto to Texas, Hotel California has boldly taken the tribute band where none had gone before them and changed an industry’s collective mind about how good a “tribute” band could really be.\nThe experience of a Hotel California show isn’t just about the band - it’s about celebrating the music and the memories, and the band gets the audiences involved and on their feet!\nClose your eyes and you’re right back there…You’ll hear all the hits, remarkably replicated, in this spectacular show!\n \nhttps://vimeo.com/1038200479\n          \n        \n              \n\n      \n  \n    Event Info\n\n          \n        Category: Music      \n    \n          \n        Genre: Tribute      \n    \n          \n        Event Length: 110 minutes\n      \n    \n      \n  \n  \t\t\n\n\n      \n      Venue\n\n              Imperial Theatre\n      \n              12 King Square South, Saint John NB, E2L 5B8\n      \n              \n          \n            View on Google Maps\n          \n        \n          \n  \n  \n\n\n\n{\n    \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n    \"@type\": \"Event\",\n    \"@id\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/hotel-california-the-original-eagles-tribute/23801AJTHHRQPTBGSQKNGJHMKGQMHTHHM/#event-23801ajthhrqptbgsqkngjhmkgqmhthhm\",\n    \"name\": \"Hotel California: The Original Eagles Tribute\",\n    \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/hotel-california-the-original-eagles-tribute/23801AJTHHRQPTBGSQKNGJHMKGQMHTHHM/\",\n    \"eventAttendanceMode\": \"https://schema.org/OfflineEventAttendanceMode\",\n    \"eventStatus\": \"https://schema.org/EventScheduled\",\n    \"location\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Place\",\n        \"name\": \"Imperial Theatre\",\n        \"sameAs\": [\n            \"http://kg.artsdata.ca/resource/K11-193\",\n            \"http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q3527482\"\n        ],\n        \"address\": {\n            \"@type\": \"PostalAddress\",\n            \"streetAddress\": \"12 King Square South\",\n            \"addressLocality\": \"Saint John\",\n            \"postalCode\": \"E2L 5B8\",\n            \"addressRegion\": \"New Brunswick\",\n            \"addressCountry\": {\n                \"@type\": \"Country\",\n                \"name\": \"CA\"\n            }\n        }\n    },\n    \"organizer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Imperial Theatre\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/\"\n    },\n    \"description\": \"A Seating $69.00 | B Seating $64.00 | C Seating $59.00 // VaughnCo Entertainment is proud to present   Hotel California - The Original Eagles Tribute When The Eagles stopped to catch their breath a few decades ago, having sold over 100 million records, collected six Grammys, and enjoyed six #1 albums, Hotel California began a pioneering journey through their history-making music that has taken them around the globe and thrilled hundreds of thousands of Eagles fans. Hotel California toured relentlessly from the 80’s straight through to today, setting the standard for world-class tribute productions as they went, and sharing stages with the likes of The Doobie Bros., Lynyrd Skynyrd, Gretchen Wilson, REO Speedwagon, and many more. From Japan to Dubai, Toronto to Texas, Hotel California has boldly taken the tribute band where none had gone before them and changed an industry’s collective mind about how good a “tribute” band could really be. The experience of a Hotel California show isn’t just about the band - it’s about celebrating the music and the memories, and the band gets the audiences involved and on their feet! Close your eyes and you’re right back there…You’ll hear all the hits, remarkably replicated, in this spectacular show!   https://vimeo.com/1038200479\",\n    \"image\": [\n        \"https://system.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/files/750e8f4e-c8d6-4ab2-9268-dd66eaef9f4a.jpg\"\n    ],\n    \"startDate\": \"2027-03-10T15:30:00-04:00\",\n    \"offers\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Offer\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatrenewbrunswick.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/website/EventDetails.aspx?EventId=23801AJTHHRQPTBGSQKNGJHMKGQMHTHHM\",\n        \"availability\": \"https://schema.org/InStock\",\n        \"validFrom\": \"2027-03-10T15:30:00-04:00\"\n    },\n    \"performer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Thing\",\n        \"additionalType\": [\n            \"http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Agent\",\n            \"http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Agent\"\n        ],\n        \"name\": \"Hotel California: The Original Eagles Tribute\"\n    }\n}\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t"
      }
    ]
