      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n          \n        \n      \n    \n\n    Thu Mar 11, 2027 • 7:30pm\n\n  \n          Music\n    \n          Classical / Orchestra\n      \n\n  Event length: 110 minutes\n\n      Admission $65.00\n    \n      Ticket prices include all taxes and fees.\n    \n  \n\n\n      \n  \n    Buy tickets\n  \n\n      \n      IT Member Event\n    \n  \n  \n  \n  \n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n    \n      \n                  The Espionage Orchestra\n        \n                  \n            $65 Regular || $60 Member ||\nThe Espionage Orchestra is the Ultimate tribute to the incredible music of the James Bond Film Empire. This 13-piece show band is stacked with some of the finest musicians in North America including the fabulous Rebecca Noelle and Michael Hanna Sr on vocals. A powerhouse horn section and elegant string quartet soar gracefully over the driving rhythm section to deliver you some of the most remarkable music ever written for film! \nFrom 'Thunderball' to 'Skyfall' you'll be captivated from the moment the curtain goes up. \nThe Espionage Orchestra is an 'Ed Lister Music' production.  Ed Lister is a Juno Award winning Trumpeter, Composer, Arranger and Educator from London, England. Now residing in Ottawa, Ed runs numerous productions and ensembles. All arrangements and orchestration for 'The Espionage Orchestra' are by Ed. You can find more info on Ed at www.edlistermusic.com \n          \n        \n              \n\n      \n  \n    Event Info\n\n          \n        Category: Music      \n    \n          \n        Genre: Classical / Orchestra      \n    \n          \n        Event Length: 110 minutes\n      \n    \n      \n  \n  \t\t\n\n\n      \n      Venue\n\n              Imperial Theatre\n      \n              12 King Square South, Saint John NB, E2L 5B8\n      \n              \n          \n            View on Google Maps\n          \n        \n          \n  \n      \n        \n    \n    \n          \n        Event Sponsor\n        \n                                        \n      \n      \n      \n  \n\n\n\n{\n    \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n    \"@type\": \"Event\",\n    \"@id\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/the-espionage-orchestra/42201AQKKRSPRKRLQJDDCVRBGKSTCCBDJ/#event-42201aqkkrsprkrlqjddcvrbgkstccbdj\",\n    \"name\": \"The Espionage Orchestra\",\n    \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/the-espionage-orchestra/42201AQKKRSPRKRLQJDDCVRBGKSTCCBDJ/\",\n    \"eventAttendanceMode\": \"https://schema.org/OfflineEventAttendanceMode\",\n    \"eventStatus\": \"https://schema.org/EventScheduled\",\n    \"location\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Place\",\n        \"name\": \"Imperial Theatre\",\n        \"sameAs\": [\n            \"http://kg.artsdata.ca/resource/K11-193\",\n            \"http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q3527482\"\n        ],\n        \"address\": {\n            \"@type\": \"PostalAddress\",\n            \"streetAddress\": \"12 King Square South\",\n            \"addressLocality\": \"Saint John\",\n            \"postalCode\": \"E2L 5B8\",\n            \"addressRegion\": \"New Brunswick\",\n            \"addressCountry\": {\n                \"@type\": \"Country\",\n                \"name\": \"CA\"\n            }\n        }\n    },\n    \"organizer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Imperial Theatre\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/\"\n    },\n    \"description\": \"$65 Regular || $60 Member || The Espionage Orchestra is the Ultimate tribute to the incredible music of the James Bond Film Empire. This 13-piece show band is stacked with some of the finest musicians in North America including the fabulous Rebecca Noelle and Michael Hanna Sr on vocals. A powerhouse horn section and elegant string quartet soar gracefully over the driving rhythm section to deliver you some of the most remarkable music ever written for film! From 'Thunderball' to 'Skyfall' you'll be captivated from the moment the curtain goes up. The Espionage Orchestra is an 'Ed Lister Music' production. Ed Lister is a Juno Award winning Trumpeter, Composer, Arranger and Educator from London, England. Now residing in Ottawa, Ed runs numerous productions and ensembles. All arrangements and orchestration for 'The Espionage Orchestra' are by Ed. You can find more info on Ed at www.edlistermusic.com\",\n    \"image\": [\n        \"https://system.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/files/7eabbd60-e222-49e0-b4f7-79e10761b3c9.jpg\"\n    ],\n    \"startDate\": \"2027-03-11T15:30:00-04:00\",\n    \"offers\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Offer\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatrenewbrunswick.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/website/EventDetails.aspx?EventId=42201AQKKRSPRKRLQJDDCVRBGKSTCCBDJ\",\n        \"availability\": \"https://schema.org/InStock\",\n        \"validFrom\": \"2027-03-11T15:30:00-04:00\"\n    },\n    \"performer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Thing\",\n        \"additionalType\": [\n            \"http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Agent\",\n            \"http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Agent\"\n        ],\n        \"name\": \"The Espionage Orchestra\"\n    }\n}\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t"
