' you'll be captivated from the moment the curtain goes up. The Espionage Orchestra is an 'Ed Lister Music' production. Ed Lister is a Juno Award winning Trumpeter, Composer, Arranger and Educator from London, England. Now residing in Ottawa, Ed runs numerous productions and ensembles. All arrangements and orchestration for 'The Espionage Orchestra' are by Ed. You can find more info on Ed at www.edlistermusic.com\",\n    \"image\": [\n        \"https://system.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/files/7eabbd60-e222-49e0-b4f7-79e10761b3c9.jpg\"\n    ],\n    \"startDate\": \"2027-03-11T15:30:00-04:00\",\n    \"offers\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Offer\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatrenewbrunswick.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/website/EventDetails.aspx?EventId=42201AQKKRSPRKRLQJDDCVRBGKSTCCBDJ\",\n        \"availability\": \"https://schema.org/InStock\",\n        \"validFrom\": \"2027-03-11T15:30:00-04:00\"\n    },\n    \"performer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Thing\",\n        \"additionalType\": [\n            \"http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Agent\",\n            \"http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Agent\"\n        ],\n        \"name\": \"The Espionage Orchestra\"\n    }\n}\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t"
