llads, crooner, and pop. Performances are backed by industry veterans who have worked with renowned acts such as Burton Cummings, Big Wreck, Moist, David Usher, Helix, and Killer Dwarfs. The Process Auditions: Held 2–3 months before the show, auditions take place in-person at the host venue. Between 80–150 people generally attend, with the team handling outreach, hosting, and selection. Selection: 15–20 singers are chosen to perform. Preparation: The team coordinates song choices and key changes with selected performers. A sound check and rehearsal occur on the day of the show. AUDITIONS will be held on the Imperial stage Sunday, July 12 9:30 -12 noon & 2-5pm. REGISTER HERE: https://www.canyousing.ca/register\",\n    \"image\": [\n        \"https://system.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/files/00f6432d-f750-44fc-a601-6902bbab1757.jpg\"\n    ],\n    \"startDate\": \"2027-03-12T15:30:00-04:00\",\n    \"offers\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Offer\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatrenewbrunswick.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/website/EventDetails.aspx?EventId=42401AMGVRNMTBVGKTCVLCNVTMNDSPQQG\",\n        \"availability\": \"https://schema.org/InStock\",\n        \"validFrom\": \"2027-03-12T15:30:00-04:00\"\n    },\n    \"performer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Thing\",\n        \"additionalType\": [\n            \"http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Agent\",\n            \"http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Agent\"\n        ],\n        \"name\": \"Can You Sing Canada presents Saint John Sings!\"\n    }\n}\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t"
