    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Adult $30.00 | Member $25.00 | Student $15.00 // The New Brunswick Youth Orchestra returns to Saint John for the finale of our 2026–2027 season. Join us for an unforgettable evening as our talented young musicians bring Igor Stravinsky's blazing masterpiece, The Firebird Suite, to life. From the mysterious, shimmering opening to its triumphant, soaring finale, The Firebird is a musical journey like no other — a work that has captivated audiences for over a century and remains one of the most thrilling pieces in the orchestral repertoire. Don't miss this spectacular close to a remarkable season."
      }
    ],
