        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n          \n        \n      \n    \n\n    Sat May 1, 2027 • 7:30pm\n\n  \n          Music\n    \n          Pop\n      \n\n  Event length: 110 minutes\n\n      Admission $67.00 | Admission $63.00 | Admission $59.00\n    \n      Ticket prices include all taxes and fees.\n    \n  \n\n\n      \n  \n    Buy tickets\n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n  \n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n    \n      \n                  Rumours: The Ultimate Fleetwood Mac Tribute Show\n        \n                  \n            A Seating $67.00 | B Seating $63.00| C Seating $59.00 //\nVaughnCo Entertainment is proud to present “Rumours” The Ultimate Fleetwood Mac tribute show\nbased in Los Angeles, California.  The group recreates the legendary band in its youthful heyday from\n1975-1979. “It’s been said imitation is the sincerest form of flattery. I say THANK YOU!”-\nRichard Dashut Record Producer - Fleetwood Mac albums including Rumours, Tusk, Live\nMirage, Tango In The Night, and Time.\nAfter finding huge success in Los Angeles, selling out their regular Roxy Theatre \nperformances month after month, the band moved from the world famous Sunset Strip to Casinos,\nTheatres, and clubs all over Canada and the United States.\n          \n        \n              \n\n      \n  \n    Event Info\n\n          \n        Category: Music      \n    \n          \n        Genre: Pop      \n    \n          \n        Event Length: 110 minutes\n      \n    \n      \n  \n  \t\t\n\n\n      \n      Venue\n\n              Imperial Theatre\n      \n              12 King Square South, Saint John NB, E2L 5B8\n      \n              \n          \n            View on Google Maps\n          \n        \n          \n  \n  \n\n\n\n{\n    \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n    \"@type\": \"Event\",\n    \"@id\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/rumours-the-ultimate-fleetwood-mac-tribute-show/27601AQVLTVTCJRHPTLCPRBPBJCDTNLPC/#event-27601aqvltvtcjrhptlcprbpbjcdtnlpc\",\n    \"name\": \"Rumours: The Ultimate Fleetwood Mac Tribute Show\",\n    \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/rumours-the-ultimate-fleetwood-mac-tribute-show/27601AQVLTVTCJRHPTLCPRBPBJCDTNLPC/\",\n    \"eventAttendanceMode\": \"https://schema.org/OfflineEventAttendanceMode\",\n    \"eventStatus\": \"https://schema.org/EventScheduled\",\n    \"location\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Place\",\n        \"name\": \"Imperial Theatre\",\n        \"sameAs\": [\n            \"http://kg.artsdata.ca/resource/K11-193\",\n            \"http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q3527482\"\n        ],\n        \"address\": {\n            \"@type\": \"PostalAddress\",\n            \"streetAddress\": \"12 King Square South\",\n            \"addressLocality\": \"Saint John\",\n            \"postalCode\": \"E2L 5B8\",\n            \"addressRegion\": \"New Brunswick\",\n            \"addressCountry\": {\n                \"@type\": \"Country\",\n                \"name\": \"CA\"\n            }\n        }\n    },\n    \"organizer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Imperial Theatre\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/\"\n    },\n    \"description\": \"A Seating $67.00 | B Seating $63.00| C Seating $59.00 // VaughnCo Entertainment is proud to present “Rumours” The Ultimate Fleetwood Mac tribute show based in Los Angeles, California.  The group recreates the legendary band in its youthful heyday from 1975-1979. “It’s been said imitation is the sincerest form of flattery. I say THANK YOU!”- Richard Dashut Record Producer - Fleetwood Mac albums including Rumours, Tusk, Live Mirage, Tango In The Night, and Time. After finding huge success in Los Angeles, selling out their regular Roxy Theatre  performances month after month, the band moved from the world famous Sunset Strip to Casinos, Theatres, and clubs all over Canada and the United States.\",\n    \"image\": [\n        \"https://system.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/files/3bac2b8b-b386-4648-9f11-cda121bae9d6.jpg\"\n    ],\n    \"startDate\": \"2027-05-01T16:30:00-03:00\",\n    \"offers\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Offer\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatrenewbrunswick.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/website/EventDetails.aspx?EventId=27601AQVLTVTCJRHPTLCPRBPBJCDTNLPC\",\n        \"availability\": \"https://schema.org/InStock\",\n        \"validFrom\": \"2027-05-01T16:30:00-03:00\"\n    },\n    \"performer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Thing\",\n        \"additionalType\": [\n            \"http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Agent\",\n            \"http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Agent\"\n        ],\n        \"name\": \"Rumours: The Ultimate Fleetwood Mac Tribute Show\"\n    }\n}\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t"
