    "https://schema.org/text": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n          \n        \n      \n    \n\n    Mon May 10, 2027 • 7:00pm\n\n  \n          Film\n    \n          Retro Film\n      \n\n  Event length: 96 minutes\n\n      Admission $10.00\n    \n      Ticket prices include all taxes and fees.\n    \n  \n\n\n      \n  \n    Buy tickets\n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n  \n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n    \n      \n                  Retro Film: Spaceballs\n        \n                  \n            Rating: PG | Year: 1987 // In a distant galaxy, planet Spaceball has depleted its air supply, leaving its citizens reliant on a product called \"Perri-Air.\" In desperation, Spaceball's leader President Skroob (Mel Brooks) orders the evil Dark Helmet (Rick Moranis) to kidnap Princess Vespa (Daphne Zuniga) of oxygen-rich Druidia and hold her hostage in exchange for air. But help arrives for the Princess in the form of renegade space pilot Lone Starr (Bill Pullman) and his half-man, half-dog partner, Barf (John Candy).\n          \n        \n              \n\n      \n  \n    Event Info\n\n          \n        Category: Film      \n    \n          \n        Genre: Retro Film      \n    \n          \n        Event Length: 96 minutes\n      \n    \n      \n  \n  \t\t\n\n\n      \n      Venue\n\n              Imperial Theatre\n      \n              12 King Square South, Saint John NB, E2L 5B8\n      \n              \n          \n            View on Google Maps\n          \n        \n          \n  \n      \n        \n    \n    \n          \n        Event Sponsor\n        \n                                        \n      \n      \n      \n  \n\n\n\n{\n    \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n    \"@type\": \"Event\",\n    \"@id\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/retro-film-spaceballs/33201AJLRJQTMSPLGKHLNMPSPGHMNLTRH/#event-33201ajlrjqtmsplgkhlnmpspghmnltrh\",\n    \"name\": \"Retro Film: Spaceballs\",\n    \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/retro-film-spaceballs/33201AJLRJQTMSPLGKHLNMPSPGHMNLTRH/\",\n    \"eventAttendanceMode\": \"https://schema.org/OfflineEventAttendanceMode\",\n    \"eventStatus\": \"https://schema.org/EventScheduled\",\n    \"location\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Place\",\n        \"name\": \"Imperial Theatre\",\n        \"sameAs\": [\n            \"http://kg.artsdata.ca/resource/K11-193\",\n            \"http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q3527482\"\n        ],\n        \"address\": {\n            \"@type\": \"PostalAddress\",\n            \"streetAddress\": \"12 King Square South\",\n            \"addressLocality\": \"Saint John\",\n            \"postalCode\": \"E2L 5B8\",\n            \"addressRegion\": \"New Brunswick\",\n            \"addressCountry\": {\n                \"@type\": \"Country\",\n                \"name\": \"CA\"\n            }\n        }\n    },\n    \"organizer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Imperial Theatre\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/\"\n    },\n    \"description\": \"$10.00 // Rating: PG | Year: 1987 // In a distant galaxy, planet Spaceball has depleted its air supply, leaving its citizens reliant on a product called \\\"Perri-Air.\\\" In desperation, Spaceball's leader President Skroob (Mel Brooks) orders the evil Dark Helmet (Rick Moranis) to kidnap Princess Vespa (Daphne Zuniga) of oxygen-rich Druidia and hold her hostage in exchange for air. But help arrives for the Princess in the form of renegade space pilot Lone Starr (Bill Pullman) and his half-man, half-dog partner, Barf (John Candy).\",\n    \"image\": [\n        \"https://system.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/files/f446183b-3a8c-467c-9246-255640e21c8b.jpg\"\n    ],\n    \"startDate\": \"2027-05-10T16:00:00-03:00\",\n    \"offers\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Offer\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatrenewbrunswick.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/website/EventDetails.aspx?EventId=33201AJLRJQTMSPLGKHLNMPSPGHMNLTRH\",\n