        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n          \n        \n      \n    \n\n    Wed May 19, 2027 • 7:30pm\n\n  \n          Theatre\n    \n          Musical\n      \n\n  Event length: 140 minutes\n\n      Adult $65.00 | Senior $60.00 | Student $35.00\n    \n      Ticket prices include all taxes and fees.\n    \n  \n\n\n      \n  \n    Buy tickets\n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n  \n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t  \n    \n      \n                  SJTC: Spamalot\n        \n                  \n            \n\tSpamalotDon’t miss Spamalot! A laugh-out-loud musical quest for the Holy Grail, where logic is optional and danger is rarely taken seriously. From “flesh wounds” that aren’t quite as bad as they look to gloriously absurd misadventures at every turn, it’s a fast-paced, joyfully ridiculous night at the theatre you won’t want to miss.Performances-Wednesday, May 19th, 2027 at 7:30pm-Thursday, May 20th 2027 at 7:30pm-Friday, May 21st, 2027 at 7:30pm-Saturday, May 22nd, 2027 at 2:00pm-Saturday, May 22nd, 2027 at 7:30pmPurchase a SJTC Subscription and save 25% off single ticket prices!We are happy to hold prior season subscribers' seats until September 1st 2026. Single tickets on sale September 1st, 2026 at noon.\n\n          \n        \n              \n\n      \n  \n    Event Info\n\n          \n        Category: Theatre      \n    \n          \n        Genre: Musical      \n    \n          \n        Event Length: 140 minutes\n      \n    \n      \n  \n  \t  \t  \n    \tPerformer Website:\n    \t\n      Visit Website\n    \t\n      \n\t\t\n\n\n      \n      Venue\n\n              Imperial Theatre\n      \n              12 King Square South, Saint John NB, E2L 5B8\n      \n              \n          \n            View on Google Maps\n          \n        \n          \n  \n  \n\n\n\n{\n    \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n    \"@type\": \"Event\",\n    \"@id\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/sjtc-spamalot/29802ARMQMGKNGMTDHGSLHRSMNMDSQQJT/#event-29802armqmgkngmtdhgslhrsmnmdsqqjt\",\n    \"name\": \"SJTC: Spamalot\",\n    \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/event/sjtc-spamalot/29802ARMQMGKNGMTDHGSLHRSMNMDSQQJT/\",\n    \"eventAttendanceMode\": \"https://schema.org/OfflineEventAttendanceMode\",\n    \"eventStatus\": \"https://schema.org/EventScheduled\",\n    \"location\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Place\",\n        \"name\": \"Imperial Theatre\",\n        \"sameAs\": [\n            \"http://kg.artsdata.ca/resource/K11-193\",\n            \"http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q3527482\"\n        ],\n        \"address\": {\n            \"@type\": \"PostalAddress\",\n            \"streetAddress\": \"12 King Square South\",\n            \"addressLocality\": \"Saint John\",\n            \"postalCode\": \"E2L 5B8\",\n            \"addressRegion\": \"New Brunswick\",\n            \"addressCountry\": {\n                \"@type\": \"Country\",\n                \"name\": \"CA\"\n            }\n        }\n    },\n    \"organizer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Imperial Theatre\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatre.ca/\"\n    },\n    \"description\": \"$65 Regular | $60 Senior | $35 Student // Don’t miss Spamalot! A laugh-out-loud musical quest for the Holy Grail, where logic is optional and danger is rarely taken seriously. From “flesh wounds” that aren’t quite as bad as they look to gloriously absurd misadventures at every turn, it’s a fast-paced, joyfully ridiculous night at the theatre you won’t want to miss.\",\n    \"image\": [\n        \"https://system.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/files/81e45df9-3031-4d02-bca4-bf0906344aa4.jpg\"\n    ],\n    \"startDate\": \"2027-05-19T16:30:00-03:00\",\n    \"offers\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Offer\",\n        \"url\": \"https://imperialtheatrenewbrunswick.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/website/EventDetails.aspx?EventId=29802ARMQMGKNGMTDHGSLHRSMNMDSQQJT\",\n        \"availability\": \"https://schema.org/InStock\",\n        \"validFrom\": \"2027-05-19T16:30:00-03:00\"\n    },\n    \"performer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Thing\",\n        \"additionalType\": [\n            \"http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Agent\",\n            \"http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Agent\"\n        ],\n        \"name\": \"SJTC: Spamalot\"\n    }\n}\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t"
